{"tid":1499760,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果有大鑊野大型衝突前全民put過夜，可唔可以拖lum個市？","createTime":"2019-08-24T00:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T00:58:55.000Z","uid":24615,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1093ec2738c9eba31c4fce7401b761d49655688e","tid":1499760,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:11:12.000Z","msg":"我諗番起當年魚革前 我put過假期， 新年開電視見到打到飛起，我係笑到嘴角合唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見黑警比人打到飛起，我d貨又升到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是諗如果有下次大鑊野（831後續，10月1end game大戰）<br />\n<br />\n全民Put（可能需要更多中產參與）<br />\n<br />\n星期一開市可唔可以造成恐慌性跌市？<br />\n又可以賺番少少錢<br />\n賺左既錢可以比受左傷/拉左既前線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前面班人玩火魔法玩得更投入（燒多兩架犬車 聽日個市就跌多幾點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，打撚死狗狗跌多一百點，當然 比狗狗開槍打都會跌多好多點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"9d9a894b67b843605bbcfa15633c254ce3feb98f","tid":1499760,"uid":24615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:12:00.000Z","msg":"最好撞埋侵生加關稅"},{"pid":"42d0b4dab8960504e85d3d06337e53b979bf78cf","tid":1499760,"uid":15009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:16:12.000Z","msg":"Call左証監<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0788c3aa5ddf4f91ad6db1a674713e9aad236fa0","tid":1499760,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42d0b4dab8960504e85d3d06337e53b979bf78cf","tid":1499760,"uid":15009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:16:12.000Z","msg":"Call左証監<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gi